      • getSearchSimpleSearchResults

        public int[] getSearchSimpleSearchResults(java.lang.String query,
                                 java.lang.String token)
        Function to call the SimpleSearch operation of ChemSpider's Search SOAP 1.2 webservice (http://www.chemspider.com/search.asmx?op=SimpleSearch) Search by Name, SMILES, InChI, InChIKey, etc. Returns a list of found CSIDs (first 100 - please use AsyncSimpleSearch instead if you like to get the full list). Security token is required.
        Parameters:
        query: - String representing search term (can be Name, SMILES, InChI, InChIKey)
        token: - string containing your user token (listed at your http://www.chemspider.com/UserProfile.aspx page)

                                                                                                                                  java.lang.String token)

      • getSearchGetAsyncSearchStatusResults

        public java.lang.String getSearchGetAsyncSearchStatusResults(java.lang.String rid,
                                                    java.lang.String token)
        Function to call the GetAsyncSearchStatus operation of ChemSpider's Search SOAP 1.2 webservice (http://www.chemspider.com/search.asmx?op=GetAsyncSearchStatus) Query asynchronous operation status. Requires transaction ID returned by AsynchSearch operation. Security token is required.
        Parameters:
        rid: - String representing transaction ID returned from a previous search
        token: - string containing your user token (listed at your http://www.chemspider.com/UserProfile.aspx page)
